snippet.title: I'm Joshua - The Diary
snippet.description:
I'm Joshua: video of the private diary.

I'm Joshua is an adventure game, point and click, set in the U.S.A. of the 19th Century.
It will be released, for PC, in three chapters.

Stay updated on I'm Joshua:

* Site: http://www.imjoshua.net/
* Twitter: https://twitter.com/ImJoshuaTheGame
* Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/joshuavideogame
* Steam Group: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/imjoshua/
* IndieDB: http://www.indiedb.com/games/im-joshua
* Press Kit: http://www.imjoshua.net/presskit/index.html
* Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?playnext=1&list=PL60afGyAEZacrN8BVDzUxjoIrJa7_Rt8S
